<L>__{interior hall (dusk) medium shot}
<A>__{the camera pans ben as he hurries forward. he touches jo lightly on the shoulder. she turns, startled, and manages to suppress an exclamation on seeing him. we do not hear what they are saying but by their pantomime we see that jo is telling ben all about the impending shooting. ben argues with her. he indicates he will tell buchanan. she frantically restrains him but he shakes her off and dashes away.}
